{"tid":788593,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一年容易又ocamp (致freshman)","createTime":"2018-08-21T14:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T15:10:28.000Z","uid":199208,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1eeb209198424a9d67cf51a19608400ba6ab8518","tid":788593,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"每年呢個時候, 總係有好多ocamp相在fb,ig 出現<br />\n到底一張張的笑臉背後, 有幾多真摯的友誼?<br />\n又有幾多獸父, 抱著其他目的, 磨刀霍霍向freshman<br />\n一年後再回想, 到底係一場青春, 定係一場笑話<br />\n我睇唔透<br />\n以老鬼身份重返ocamp, 係想再一次體驗熱血, 定係想趕在畢業前出pool?<br />\n<br />\n大學的生涯, 最大的得著, 係體驗左人性的黑暗同醜陋<br />\n你可能會被出賣, 被背叛<br />\n可能十年後你都仍然會無法釋懷<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐, 我想講的係:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街啦獸父! 小白臉! 忍左你好耐啦! 咁多人死唔見你死!</span><br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"6e4ee9b1a4666b6313e0aa924e88d6a4b78188ae","tid":788593,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"唔開名咁你開post係想屌邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef8b0fada08be506909e190af126123c2b78126","tid":788593,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"返名校secrets啦 1999你老母個臭閪咩"},{"pid":"2a1f33af5cf2f54945e22baba582d53ef04a7fb8","tid":788593,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e4ee9b1a4666b6313e0aa924e88d6a4b78188ae","tid":788593,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"唔開名咁你開post係想屌邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"我要屌曬所有獸父獸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}